<section id="section-4a">
<title> Obtaining expression of velocity in time, “t”
</title>
<para id="element-48">

The acceleration is defined as :



</para>
<para id="element-50">
Arranging terms with same variable on one side of the equation, we have :

</para>
<para id="element-51">
<m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mo>đ</m:mo>
    <m:mi>t</m:mi>
    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
    <m:mfrac>
      <m:mrow>
        <m:mo>đ</m:mo>
        <m:mi>v</m:mi>
      </m:mrow>
      <m:mrow>
        <m:mi>a</m:mi>
        <m:mfenced>
          <m:mrow>
