</para>
<para id="element-357">
Thus, the maximum velocity during motion under this condition is 2 m/s. On the other hand, the acceleration for this motion is equal to the slope of the line,
</para>
<para id="element-358">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
