<m:mn> 25 </m:mn>
<m:mi> m </m:mi>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-419">
<figure id="fig-419">
<title> Displacement – time plot  </title>
<media id="idm4967136" alt=""><image src="../../media/amo2.gif" mime-type="image/gif"/></media>
<caption> Corresponding displacement – time plot of the given velocity- - time plot. </caption>
</figure>
</para>
<para id="element-420">The velocity between 2 and 4 s is increasing at constant rate. The acceleration, therefore, is constant and its magnitude is equal to the slope of the plot, 
<m:math>
<m:mfrac bevelled="true">
<m:mn> 20 </m:mn>
